{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-323-bitwise-or-operations-on-random-integers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 323: Operacije bitwise-OR na nasumičnim celobrojnim brojevima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka su $y_0, y_1, y_2, \\ldots$ sekvenca slučajnih bezznakom 32-bit celih brojeva (tj. $0 ≤ y_i &#x3C; 2^{32}$, svaka vrednost ima jednaku verovatnoću).</p>\n<p>Za niz $x_i$, data je sledeća rekurentna relacija:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$x_0 = 0$ za</li>\n<li>$x_i = x_{i - 1} \\mathbf{|} y_{i - 1}$, za $i > 0$. ($\\mathbf{|}$ je bitwise OR operacija)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Izgleda da konačno postoji model $N$ takav da $x_i = 2^{32} - 1$ (obrazac svih bita je jedinica) za svako $i \\ge N$.</p>\n<p>Pronađite očekivanu vrednost za $N$. Navedite svoj odgovor zaokružen na 10 decimalnih mesta.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4b01000cf542c50ffc2","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301980,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-323-bitwise-or-operations-on-random-integers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function bitwiseOrOnRandomIntegers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nbitwiseOrOnRandomIntegers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>bitwiseOrOnRandomIntegers()</code> treba da vrati <code>6.3551758451</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(bitwiseOrOnRandomIntegers(), 6.3551758451);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-